{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515640/extras/Arcade_gameplay_650x338_25fps.gif?t=1739481934\" /><br>Gilly, the owner of a local arcade, is trying to save his business from a faceless mega-corporation, Fun Fun Co. ...and what better way to stick it to the man than with a brand-spanking-new super game. Unfortunately, the corp gets wind of Gilly\u2019s plan and launches a cyberattack, injecting a virus into the game. Now it\u2019s up to you, will you rise up to save both the game and the last remaining local arcade?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515640/extras/Horde_Intro_Cinematic.gif?t=1739481934\" /><br><br>This ever-evolving co-op multiplayer, roguelite shooter allows you and up to 3 friends to explore multiple biomes, compete in mini games, find hidden chests, and battle a crazy cast of enemies and bosses. Arcadegeddon lets you play at your own pace with its mix of PVE and PVP gameplay. Speed into the action or take it slow, it\u2019s up to you. As you get to know the town, you can dive into additional challenges from the local gangs that hangout in Gilly\u2019s Arcade, earning you much more than just street cred. Though, the view from the top of the leaderboards must be pretty darn good...<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515640/extras/Outfits.gif?t=1739481934\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515640/extras/Weapons.gif?t=1739481934\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515640/extras/Chest.gif?t=1739481934\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Adventure Time","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1515640/438e95e61c53d7a41db2106bce737176ee7d7776.jpg"},{"na